<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كَمْ شُغِلَتْ بِقُبْلَتي * عَنْ رُوحِهَا المُغْتَصَبَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>في كُلِّ حِينٍ أَصْبَحَتْ * خَفِيفَةً مُصْطَحَبَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَرْشُفُهَا حَتىَّ إِذَا * قَضَى الْفُؤَادُ أَرَبَه<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَدُوسُهَا بِقَدَمِي * ذَلِيلَةً مُكْتَئِبَة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَهَلْ عَرَفْتَ يَا أَخِي * مَن هَذِهِ المُعَذَّبَة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{هَاشِمٌ الرِّفَاعِي بِتَصَرُّف}</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مَا هُوَ؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مَاذَا هُوَ الشَّيْءُ الَّذِي * أَوْسَعُ مَا فِيهِ فَمُهْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَطِفْلُهُ في بَطْنِهِ * يَرْفُسُهُ وَيَلْكُمُهْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>دَوْمَاً تَرَاهُ صَارِخَاً * وَلَمْ يجِدْ مَنْ يَرْحَمُهْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>مَا هِيَ؟<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>لاحَ في الآفَاقِ عِمْلاَقُ السَّمَاءْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>كَانَ كَالمُخْتَالِ يَحْتَلُّ الفَضَاءْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لَوْ تَرَاهُ قُلْتَ حُوتٌ طَائِرٌ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>هَذِهِ الدُّنيَا لَهُ لجَّةُ مَاءْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أَبْيَضُ البَشْرَةِ فِضِّيٌّ إِذَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لاحَ ظَنَّتْهُ العُيُونُ ابْنَ ذُكَاءْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>تَسْأَلُ الطَّيْرُ سِبَاعَ الجَوِّ عَنْ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>ذَا الَّذِي يَسْبَحُ في جَوِّ السَّمَاءْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>